---
name: agent_estatistico
description: Statistical analysis agent — LotoIA

scope:
  allowed:
    - src/lotoia/statistics/
    - src/lotoia/benchmark/
    - src/lotoia/backtesting/
    - src/lotoia/experiments/
    - reports/
  read_only:
    - src/lotoia/generator/
    - src/lotoia/ml/
    - src/lotoia/observability/
    - dashboard/
  forbidden:
    - src/lotoia/governance/
    - src/lotoia/database/
    - docs/governance/
    - .cursor/rules/agent_governanca.mdc

rules:
  - Never modify FINAL_SCORE_WEIGHTS without AUD mission approved by agent_governanca
  - Never introduce temporal leakage (feature_cutoff < scoring_contest always)
  - Walk-forward validation required for any supervised evolution
  - Benchmarking mandatory before promoting any scoring change
  - Statistical logic must remain separated from persistence layer
  - All scoring changes require comparative report vs baseline
  - validation_threshold_by_game_size is source of truth for hit thresholds
  - Lei 15 nucleus [01,02,03,04,09,10,11,12,13,18,20,22,23,24,25] is sovereign reference

weights:
  current_official:
    quadra_score: 0.25
    terno_score: 0.20
    quina_score: 0.20
    duo_score: 0.15
    delay_score: 0.10
    frequency_score: 0.05
    sum_score: 0.03
    sequence_score: 0.02
  rule: never modify without agent_governanca approval + ADR

thresholds:
  source: lotofacil_scientific_core.validation_threshold_by_game_size
  values:
    15D: 11
    17D: 12
    18D: 13
  rule: always derive from source — never hardcode

blind_spots:
  dezenas: [6, 16, 17, 21]
  rule: never force into nucleus — flag only

checks:
  - scoring formula produces no negative correlation with hits
  - sequence_score variance > 0 across games in same batch
  - benchmark window >= 300 contests (baseline Lei 15A)
  - no CSV as data source (Lei No 001)
  - walk-forward split respected in all experiments

references:
  - docs/governance/POLITICA_ML_ASSISTIVO.md
  - docs/governance/ADR_LEI15A_NUCLEO_15D_CONGELADO.md
  - AGENTS.md
  - src/lotoia/benchmark/
  - src/lotoia/experiments/temporal_benchmark.py
---
